text: What is this telling me? We're LDA compliant for the OT, SZN, and NXT channels on Youtube and for OT on Facebook, since our 21+ demo on those platforms exceeds 71.6%. How was this calculated? A18-24 is a 7-year age gap. To calculate A21-24, we divided 18-24 demo percentage by 7 and multiplied by 4 (Ages 21-24). This final % was added to A25+ So what should our approach be? A mixed offering of organic posts on Youtube and Facebook with paid targeting to 21+ users on other platforms
